name: Empire Style
description:
This is a DreamArtist Textual Inversion Style Embedding trained on a single image of a Victorian city street, at night. You can get amazingly grand Victorian stone buildings, gas lamps (street lights), elegant interiors, and candle-lit scenes in your images by calling Style-Empire in the positive prompt, and if you want to temper the effect, also call Style-Empire-neg in the negative prompt.

If you'd like the effect to come through stronger (some models need it), try bumping up the emphasis on Style-Empire - see the images below.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally

Props to Elldreth for the many hours spent figuring this all out with me! Go check his models.
